OL,7,FA "rising star" prison governor who
OL,8,Fbegan a relationship with a drug gang
OL,9,Fboss is facing jail after being
OL,10,Fconvicted of misconduct in a public
OL,11,Foffice.
OL,13,FKerri Pegg, 42, accepted a #12,000
OL,14,FMercedes car from Anthony Saunderson,
OL,15,Fwhich he paid for in drugs, after
OL,16,Fapproving him for temporary early
OL,17,Frelease from HMP Kirkham, Lancashire,
OL,18,Fwhere she was governor.
