OL,7,FDivorcee Pegg, described in court as,
OL,8,F"petite, blonde and bubbly", had been
OL,9,F"naive and gullible", and was taken
OL,10,Fadvantage of by Saunderson, a major
OL,11,Forganised crime boss in Liverpool, who
OL,12,Fis now serving 35 years behind bars.
OL,14,FSaunderson was known to criminal
OL,15,Fassociates as "Jesse Pinkman", the
OL,16,Fdrug dealer in Breaking Bad, or "James
OL,17,FGandolfini", the actor who played Tony
OL,18,FSoprano in the mafia TV series.
