OL,7,FPegg was seen as a "rising star" in
OL,8,Fthe Prison Service, quickly climbing
OL,9,Fthe career ladder from graduate
OL,10,Fentrant to prison governor in six
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FDuring her trial at Preston Crown
OL,14,FCourt, it emerged Saunderson had
OL,15,Fdeveloped and delivered a programme,
OL,16,Ftitled BADD (Beating Alcohol and Drug
OL,17,FDependency) for inmates at several
OL,18,Fjails ` while at the time being a
OL,19,Fmajor drug dealer, running an
OL,20,Famphetamines factory.
OL,26,@oD@TOUoD@`O]
