OL,7,FPegg claimed her contact with
OL,8,FSaunderson was due to his involvement
OL,9,Fin the BADD programme.
OL,11,FBut even members of his gang grumbled
OL,12,Fthat their boss was spending too much
OL,13,Ftime with Pegg and away from his wife
OL,14,Fand "work".
OL,16,FPegg, who also underwent breast
OL,17,Fenhancement surgery during her six
OL,18,Fyears in the service, was convicted of
OL,19,Ftwo counts of misconduct in a public
OL,20,Foffice and one count of possession of
OL,21,Fcriminal property.
