OL,7,FThe jury was out for two hours and 43
OL,8,Fminutes, following a three-week trial.
OL,10,FPegg made no reaction as the guilty
OL,11,Fverdicts were delivered.
OL,13,FJudge Graham Knowles told Pegg a
OL,14,Fprison term was "inevitable", but
OL,15,Fbailed the defendant to the court
OL,16,Fbuilding while a sentencing date is
OL,17,Farranged either later on Tuesday or at
OL,18,Fa later date.
