OL,7,FThe court heard that Pegg, originally
OL,8,Ffrom Bramhall, Stockport, had worked
OL,9,Fin the Probation Service for eight
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FMarried at 26 and divorced four years
OL,13,Flater after her husband's building and
OL,14,Frenovations firm went bust, she
OL,15,Fswitched to the Prison Service for a
OL,16,Fnew challenge.
