OL,7,FPegg joined in 2012 as a graduate
OL,8,Fentrant, working at prisons including
OL,9,FRisley, Liverpool and Styal, and by
OL,10,FApril 2018 she was a governor at HMP
OL,11,FKirkham, where Saunderson was reaching
OL,12,Fthe end of 10-year sentence for drugs
OL,13,Foffences.
OL,15,FHe had been one of Merseyside's most
OL,16,Fwanted fugitives for his part in
OL,17,Fimporting #19 million of cocaine in
OL,18,Fshipments of corned beef from
OL,19,FArgentina.
