OL,7,FFrom the start of her time at the jail
OL,8,Fthere were concerns about Pegg being
OL,9,Finappropriately close to Saunderson,
OL,10,Fwith the two often being in her office
OL,11,Fwith the door closed.
OL,13,FShe told jurors there were "cultural
OL,14,Fissues" at the jail and clashed with
OL,15,Fbosses over her "progressive" and
OL,16,F"hands-on" open-door policy with
OL,17,Fprisoners.
