OL,7,FIn October 2018, Saunderson put in a
OL,8,Frelease on temporary licence (ROTL)
OL,9,Frequest which Pegg signed off, though
OL,10,Fshe did not have the authority to do
OL,11,Fso.
OL,13,FSaunderson was released from Kirkham
OL,14,Fin May 2019 and within two months,
OL,15,Fwhile still on licence, was involved
OL,16,Fin another massive drug conspiracy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/18
