OL,7,FPegg's trial heard that he continued
OL,8,Fcontact with prisons in the BADD
OL,9,Fprogramme and was also still close to
OL,10,FPegg, who was at the time the regional
OL,11,Fofficial co-ordinating drug strategy
OL,12,Fin six prisons in the North West.
OL,14,FThe Prison Service has been contacted
OL,15,Ffor comment.
OL,17,FSaunderson and his gang were producing
OL,18,Fand supplying drugs on an industrial
OL,19,Fscale from a lab at a premises on the
OL,20,FEngland/Wales border and a storage
OL,21,Funit in Aintree, Merseyside.
