OL,7,FHe was jailed for 35 years at
OL,8,FLiverpool Crown Court in August 2022
OL,9,Fafter law enforcement agencies cracked
OL,10,Fthe Encrochat system, the phone
OL,11,Fnetwork used by serious organised
OL,12,Fcriminals.
OL,14,FIt revealed Saunderson's drug dealing
OL,15,Fand his relationship with Pegg.
OL,17,FPolice raided her apartment in Orrell,
OL,18,FWigan, in November 2020. The Mercedes
OL,19,Fpaid for by Saunderson was parked
OL,20,Foutside.
