OL,7,FThey discovered designer clothes,
OL,8,Fhandbags and jewellery, and found Pegg
OL,9,Fliving way beyond her means, buying
OL,10,FJimmy Choo shoes and Chanel necklaces.
OL,12,FDetectives discovered that despite her
OL,13,F#3,000 a month income, Pegg was deep
OL,14,Fin debt and had not declared three
OL,15,FCounty Court judgments which amounted
OL,16,Fto misconduct, as debts make officials
OL,17,Fvulnerable to corruption.
OL,19,FHer four credit cards were "maxed out"
OL,20,Fand she had 6p in her savings account.
