OL,7,FDetectives also found a toothbrush and
OL,8,Fa pair of Hugo Boss flip flops both
OL,9,Fcarrying Saunderson's DNA.
OL,11,FAndrew Alty, defending, in his closing
OL,12,Fspeech to the jury, claimed Pegg had
OL,13,Fbeen, "green and stupid" and a naive
OL,14,Fand gullible person who was
OL,15,Fmanipulated by Saunderson.
OL,17,FPegg tearfully told jurors she had
OL,18,Fbeen "incredibly stupid" but did not
OL,19,Fthink she had done anything wrong.
