OL,7,FBarbara-Louise Webster, prosecuting,
OL,8,Fsaid Pegg had a promising future, but
OL,9,Fadded: "Anthony Saunderson was her
OL,10,Fdownfall."
OL,12,FOutside court, Tarryn McCaffrey, from
OL,13,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS),
OL,14,Fsaid: "Kerri Pegg's conduct fell far
OL,15,Fshort of what might be expected from
OL,16,Fany professional within the Prison
OL,17,FService, let alone one of such a
OL,18,Fsenior grade as prison governor.
