OL,7,F"She was clearly involved in an
OL,8,Finappropriate relationship with
OL,9,FSaunderson after he was released and
OL,10,Fthe evidence points to this going back
OL,11,Ffurther, to a time when he was in jail.
OL,13,F"This relationship, and the fact that
OL,14,FPegg failed to disclose her debts to
OL,15,Fher employers, amount to a gross
OL,16,Fbreach of trust and are therefore
OL,17,Fextremely damaging to public
OL,18,Fconfidence."
