OL,7,F"We became aware of her arrest in May
OL,8,F2023, at which time we took immediate
OL,9,Fand professional HR and safeguarding
OL,10,Fadvice to guide our response. We
OL,11,Fcarefully considered all available
OL,12,Foptions, including dismissal,
OL,13,Fsuspension, and working with
OL,14,Frestrictions, while awaiting the
OL,15,Foutcome of the ongoing police
